OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fwith some patchy cloudy to the north.
OL,7,FLight winds may allow some mist to
OL,8,Fdevelop in spots. Feeling mild with
OL,9,Ftemperatures staying above average.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAny mist and fog will lift
OL,12,Fquickly, leaving a bright and sunny
OL,13,Fday for all. Feeling hot in the strong
OL,14,Fsunshine, especially in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FRemaining dry with plenty of strong
OL,18,FJuly sunshine. Feeling hot by day with
OL,19,Fnights also turning increasingly warm.
